FBIS4-29515 "dreas118_n_94023" FBIS-EAS-94-118 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 Vietnam Department Discusses Training of Lecturers Department Discusses Training of Lecturers BK1906133694 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 1100 GMT 17 Jun 94 BK1906133694 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network Vietnamese BFN [Text] The party Central Committee's Science and Ideology Department recently held a seminar in Ho Chi Minh on the planning and training of the contingent of lecturers on Marxism-Leninism and on Ho Chi Minh thought. Participants noted that the contingent of lecturers on Marxism-Leninism have contributed greatly to equipping the people with insights into Marxism-Leninism and Ho Chi Minh thought while teaching revolutionary concepts for the younger generation, party cadres and members, and the working people.
